humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: According to the report, two lymph nodes were examined and both were negative for metastatic carcinoma (0/1 for each lymph node). Therefore, the N stage for this patient is N0, which indicates no metastases in regional lymph nodes.

humanMachineDialogue.author: ZS Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The report indicates that two sentinel lymph nodes were biopsied and both were negative for metastatic carcinoma (0/1). This means that there is no evidence of cancer in the lymph nodes, which corresponds to an N0 stage.
